OL,3,C#20K Reward offered as police revisit
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb scene
OL,6,FPSNI officers have stopped cars and
OL,7,Fhanded out leaflets in Dunmurry after
OL,8,Fa #20,000 reward was offered for
OL,9,Finformation about the car bomb attack
OL,10,Fon a police station.
OL,12,FThe force revisited the town near
OL,13,FBelfast on Saturday night ` exactly
OL,14,Ftwo weeks after they had to evacuate
OL,15,Ffamilies, including young children,
OL,16,Fafter they were alerted to the
OL,17,Fexplosive.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
