OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778523070
OL,3,C#20K Reward offered as police revisit
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb scene
OL,6,FDetectives are continuing to
OL,7,Finvestigate the incident and on
OL,8,FSaturday night spoke to drivers in the
OL,9,Farea as part of their appeal for
OL,10,Finformation.
OL,12,FAt around 10.45pm on April 25, a
OL,13,Fdelivery driver was threatened by a
OL,14,Fmasked gunman in the Summerhill area
OL,15,Fof Twinbrook, the PSNI said.
OL,17,FHis vehicle was hijacked, a gas
OL,18,Fcanister-type bomb was put in the back
OL,19,Fof his car, and he was told he had 30
OL,20,Fminutes to get to Dunmurry police
OL,21,Fstation before the bomb would go off.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778523070
OL,3,C#20K Reward offered as police revisit
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb scene
OL,6,FThe driver raised the alarm and, as
OL,7,Fthe area was being evacuated, the
OL,8,Fdevice exploded at around 11.15pm.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Campbell, from the
OL,11,FPSNI's Terrorism Investigation Unit,
OL,12,Fsaid: "This cowardly and senseless
OL,13,Fattack, which could have claimed so
OL,14,Fmany innocent lives, sent shockwaves
OL,15,Facross the community.
OL,17,F"The fact that local residents,
OL,18,Fincluding two babies, were being taken
OL,19,Fto safety by officers when the device
OL,20,Fexploded speaks volumes."
OL,26,@tD@GOUyD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778523070
OL,3,C#20K Reward offered as police revisit
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb scene
OL,6,FOn Saturday night, officers
OL,7,Finvestigating the attack revisited the
OL,8,Fscene, carried out road stops,
OL,9,Fdistributed appeal leaflets and spoke
OL,10,Fwith pedestrians, drivers and
OL,11,Fpassengers.
OL,13,FMr Campbell said: "I'm asking you to
OL,14,Fthink, for just one minute, of the
OL,15,Futter devastation that could have
OL,16,Fresulted. And I'm asking you to do the
OL,17,Fright thing.
OL,19,F"If you have any information, no
OL,20,Fmatter how insignificant it might
OL,21,Fseem, please speak to us."
OL,26,@uD@SOU{D@AOU}D@ZO]
