OL,3,C#20K Reward offered as police revisit
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb scene
OL,6,FThe independent charity Crimestoppers
OL,7,Fhas offered a reward of up to #20,000
OL,8,Ffor information received directly that
OL,9,Fleads to the arrest and conviction of
OL,10,Fthose responsible for the attack.
OL,12,FOne person has appeared in court in
OL,13,Frelation to the incident.
OL,15,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,16,Fhere.
